## Admin Dashboard

### Dashboard Widget Data
All stats come from a single aggregation query — do not make N separate queries.

```typescript
// src/services/admin-dashboard.service.ts
async getSummary(): Promise<DashboardSummary> {
  return adminDashboardRepository.getAggregatedStats();
}
```

```sql
-- src/repositories/admin-dashboard.repository.ts
SELECT
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM users WHERE is_active = TRUE) AS total_users,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM articles WHERE status = 'Published' AND deleted_at IS NULL) AS published_articles,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM articles WHERE status = 'Pending' AND deleted_at IS NULL) AS pending_reviews,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tech_talks WHERE status = 'Published' AND deleted_at IS NULL) AS tech_talks;
```

### Dashboard Types
```typescript
interface DashboardSummary {
  totalUsers: number;
  publishedArticles: number;
  pendingReviews: number;        // highlight if > 0 with a badge
  techTalks: number;
}
```

