## Homepage Thread

### What to Display
Chronological feed combining **Published articles** AND **Published tech talks** sorted by `created_at DESC` (or `event_date DESC` for tech talks — use published/created date for articles).

```typescript
// src/services/homepage.service.ts
async getThread(page = 1, limit = 20): Promise<FeedItem[]> {
  // Union query — articles and tech talks in one sorted feed
  const articles = await articleRepository.findPublished({ limit, page });
  const techTalks = await techTalkRepository.findPublished({ limit, page });

  return [...articles.items, ...techTalks.items]
    .sort((a, b) => new Date(b.createdAt).getTime() - new Date(a.createdAt).getTime())
    .slice(0, limit);
}
```

